76561198092131232,Not Recommended,304730,19143725,"Posted: 18 November, 2015",all,May,"Very promising game with beautiful graphics. But to make it short: it doesn't work.Economy doesn't work------------------------------Connecting two really close cities by train can take the train up to two years game time to travel from one station to the other. You pay train maintenance several times just to transport a handful of passengers over a short distance. Silly enough since the train only shows up every two years it is nearly impossible to attract passengers. The same applies for goods but even worse, instead of waiting for your trunk, the cargo travels by itself to its destination.Transportation doesn't work:------------------------------There is no way to schedule trains or trunks so over time they will always mass up behind each other meanting that the first vehicle makes profit and the rest dosen't. But since one vehicle by itself cannot transport sufficient cargo, factories do not upgrade. Instead, cargo travels mystically by itself to its destination.The same applies for passenger trains. The first train takes all the passengers and therefore takes longer to load / unload. The next train will instantyl follow up and thus does not gain anything. And since all your trains are waiting behind the one serving the most passengers, all other stations in the rail line are not served at all!  No matter how many efford you spend on sending your trains, it will always turn out that way- there is no way to shedule trains in any way.Building doesn't work:------------------------------You can spend hours (real time) trying to figure out how to build road overpasses, tunnels ramps etc. because you cannot do it in one step and the game will randomly tell you ""terrain does not align"" or prevent you in other ways to build what you whant. Futhermore each attempt creates landscape artefacts which do not only look silly but prevent you even more from building road or rail connections.The developers spend a lot of efford in this game and keep it updated ever since. But I'm trying to play this games for almost a year now and although a lot of changes are made, no real improvemetns to the core problems came up. I really tried to like this game due its beautiful graphics but again: it doesn't work."
