re out the loan program to get enough funds to complete rail between 2 cities, and add some bus stops within the cities to get people to my stations, then paid off my loans so I can just build now in the black.Due to the enormous amount of problems and glitches with this game, I still have to rate it a thumbs down. Here's hoping for significant updates at some point."
