 passengers on the train (16 of 18 it reports) and passengers now waiting on the station is 22. I'm like, what?!? Where are those numbers coming from? It also seems that, as that train is moving to the next station, the numbers drop. 15 of 18, 14 of 18... what are they doing, jumping from the train at 40 km/h? That's suicide!Yep, I said km/h. Even though there's all British style names in the game, such as Letchworth Garden City, Totnes and Dursley, the game only allows km/h, there's no settings to change it to mph."
